description: This is a trivia to test Alexa skill. It is based on the important events with my wife-to-be 'Miriam'. This is using the trivia game template so in order to play with this, you a need an alexa-enabled device. Any hardware requirements should support this very small application.
exampleInteractions: Alexa Open rub n. miri trivia
name: "Rub & Miri" Trivia
shortDescription: A trivia of Rub & Miri for Alexa
